graph LR
    A[Collect Metrics] -->|Prometheus / Metrics Server| B[Analyze actual vs requested]
    B -->|VPA Recommendations / Kubecost| C{Is Slack Waste > 20%?}
    C -->|No| D[Keep Configuration]
    C -->|Yes| E[Recommend Resize]
    E --> F{Apply Strategy?}
